7 An Act relating to public finance; amending 62 O.S.
2021, Section 34.2, which relates to revenue
8 information; modifying provisions related to
information provided by certain state government
9 entities; modifying provisions related to information
provided to the State Board of Equalization;
10 providing an effective date; and declaring an
emergency.
